Download the App
Request your taxi in just a few seconds!
Our application is super easy and user-friendly. Just pick your current location and destination, choose the type of car you want to use and it will be at your doorstep in minutes.
Easy, reliable, and convenient:
01
Download the app and register as a new user. You can also sign in if you are already an account.
02
Choose your current location and your destination. You can change your automatically detected location by unlocking the map.
03
Choose the type of car you want to order and it will be infront of you in just few minutes.
Download Now:
The app is available for: Android and iOS!
You can easily install it on your device from the buttons below!
